{"tid":736661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首次有考生因作弊被取消所有中學文憑試科目成績","createTime":"2018-07-10T11:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T13:03:33.000Z","uid":80516,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"433333cd5e7c54d321dec224edb77e8aef4e98ac","tid":736661,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試明日放榜，今年首次有考生因作弊，被取消所有科目的考試成績。<br />\n<br />\n有一名考生被發現於考試期間，身上藏有大量與應考科目有關的筆記及小紙條，被定為嚴重違規。試場主任要求對方交出身上物品，該名考生亦承認有關行為，被考評局定為蓄意作弊，並取消文憑試所有科目成績。<br />\n<br />\n另外，考評局今年接獲79宗違反手提電話規則的個案，與去年相若，當中有兩名考生成績被降級。<br />\n<br />\n考評局公開考試總監李王鍏表示，今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包，亦有家長在口試期間致電關心考生。李王鍏提醒家長關心子女考試情況，宜改善溝通，盡量避免在考生到達考場後致電。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406201-20180710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406201-20180710.htm&d=hFCwhsiXD8p2qbGD2KRdAb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=081acdab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406201-20180710.htm&h=cd0894a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406201-20180710.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n00後既，如果你地唔想再俾人話有原罪俾人睇死既話，爭氣少少好嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都接近成年 但連一場咁重要既考試都咁多錯漏失誤 又心術不正 仲創埋被dq既歷史 00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2f3dd33d30e5abefff0932a170de7799d479c8","tid":736661,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> band 3"},{"pid":"3fc93cd5f9cb090f993bcab277c6cf45cf250b3a","tid":736661,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"熄機都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b37a0bbf9df16f9f01252010eeb841813e852ea","tid":736661,"uid":191926,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包，亦有家長在口試期間致電關心考生。李王鍏提醒家長關心子女考試情況，宜改善溝通，盡量避免在考生到達考場後致電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2073a5bc3f19bfac8b8b99e9d2306ccd05e3c9","tid":736661,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"不如估下放榜後有幾多個排隊上IFC重練人生"},{"pid":"1c0422d56a6b8b5eed65e670a5bf1f7309a3aba0","tid":736661,"uid":2772,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"9b37a0bbf9df16f9f01252010eeb841813e852ea","tid":736661,"uid":191926,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包，亦有家長在口試期間致電關心考生。李王鍏提醒家長關心子女考試情況，宜改善溝通，盡量避免在考生到達考場後致電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"被家長將手機放進書包<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味咁都有人信"},{"pid":"a374eaef6f58b98791f4f25cafb209d30d2a7382","tid":736661,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecfb64fbf2cfe4064fa7748e5f61c5fa352f1d1b","tid":736661,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b37a0bbf9df16f9f01252010eeb841813e852ea","tid":736661,"uid":191926,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包，亦有家長在口試期間致電關心考生。李王鍏提醒家長關心子女考試情況，宜改善溝通，盡量避免在考生到達考場後致電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"應該衰係收卷果時啦<br />\n見佢咁有耐未出黎<br />\n一打就出事"},{"pid":"37455be72ab5cbb96bd021d998395eb080863596","tid":736661,"uid":46927,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"1c0422d56a6b8b5eed65e670a5bf1f7309a3aba0","tid":736661,"uid":2772,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"q